---
title: Cal Smart Chicken Florentine with Lemon-Garlic Roasted Zucchini
description: This classic creamy chicken dish finds a new friend in lemony roasted zucchini – it's the perfect treat-yourself-meal for those nights where you deserve a little decadence in your life!

